    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, this specimen represents the pinnacle of the S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six has undergone a comprehensive technical refresh, including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and treated rod bearing replacement for long-term mechanical integrity. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension system that retains factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings. The exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing no signs of oxidation, while the cabin maintains its original matte finish and tactile feedback. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
