      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather is supple with no creasing, the factory scent remains, and every electronic component functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with all services documented in a comprehensive history folder. Included are all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a turnkey, investment-quality piece that satisfies even the most discerning enthusiast.",
